:::Bluestreak/Andromeda/Ratchet:::

::Bluestreak and Andromeda are about to follow the trainers, but Ratchet hold 
them back::
Ratchet: Dont, if i know Striker he'll porbably find a way out of this.
Bluestreak: But were still no better off!  I mean, We still have someone in 
the base who is plotting to kill us.
Andromeda: Without Striker and Spears, we can do nothing but wait.
::Bluestreak puts his hand on her shoulder::
Bluestreak: Dont worry, none of us are going to end up dead.  I can feel it 
inside me.
Ratchet: Man, this is mushy.
::He returns to his job of fixing the ark. He sees Rhinox::
Ratchet: Hey Rhinox? can ya help me out here?
